						<summary>

						<p>On a stone built into the bastion in the Buruzu-Āñjanēya temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Khara, Āśvija ba. 10.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of a fort by Rāja Śrī Ākunūri Narasanna and that Śirigiri Śeṭṭi Perumāḷḷu supervised the construction.</p>						

